name: CustomConditionalFormat
description: Represents a custom conditional format type.

properties.name: rule
properties.description: Represents the Rule object on this conditional format.

properties.name: format
properties.description: Returns a format object, encapsulating the conditional formats font, fill, borders, and other properties.

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fills the proxy object created in JavaScript layer with property and object values specified in the parameter.

parameters.name: param
parameters.description: Accepts parameter and relationship names as delimited string or an array. Or, provide [loadOption](loadoption.md) object.
